      "status": "wontfix",
      "note": "Standard component library barrel pattern \u2014 each component has an index.ts that re-exports from its implementation file. This is an intentional architectural convention for clean import paths (import from component/index rather than component/Component). The theme-provider barrel similarly re-exports from ThemeProvider.tsx, useTheme.ts, and types.ts.",
